title: Agent Discounts on Central Holidays Cuban Tours
text:
Agent Discounts on Central Holidays Cuban Tours July 31, 2015 
Central Holidays is offering five people-to-people tours in Cuba. The tours, which range from five to nine nights, start in Nov. 2015 and run until Dec. 2016. The itineraries include a nine-day tour called L’Chaim Cuba, which includes a visit to Ernest Hemingway's winter home in Havana, and a 10-day tour called Afro Cubanismo, which takes guests from Havana to Santiago de Cuba and Camagüey. Central Holidays is offering agents who book for themselves $1,000 savings on the tours and $750 off for travel companions. For full details, go here . 0
